Subject: Rope Basics: The Bedroom & Beyond
Description: This is a hands-on rope workshop that will quickly teach basic rope skills for the bedroom. Learn safe ways to tie someone to a bed or restrict their movement. A limited amount of rope will be available for loan. This panel is for ages 18+ only. Minors are not allowed (with or without a parent).  Speakers include:kernelbrandon - Track: After Dark  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Rope for Decoration and Restraint
Description: Learn the ins and outs of a few basic harnesses and how to integrate more decorative knotwork into your rope ties. There will be some discussion of flow in a rope scene. A limited amount of rope will be available for loan. This panel is for ages 18+ only. Minors are not allowed (with or without a parent).  Speakers include:kernelbrandon - Track: After Dark  - Duration: 50 minutes
